    <item>
      <title>为什么我认为《百年孤独》当成一本纯粹的小说看待是可以被允许的</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%88%91%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E5%BD%93%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%AC%E7%BA%AF%E7%B2%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%85%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E7%9A%84/</link>
